    "body": "### Problem\n\nThere is no stable API for setting window-local extmarks.\n\nRelevant links:\n- #19654 - initial issue for window-local extmarks.\n- #27361 - initial implementation of features that also make window-local extmarks possible.\n- #28432 - marking the initial implementation as experimental.\n- #28728 - introduction of more general and experimental `nvim__ns_{set,get}()` functions.\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nFunctions `nvim_ns_get()` and `nvim_ns_set()` are not private and not experimental.\n\nThis is a feature request and not a PR because in [this comment](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/19654#issuecomment-3618461396) @justinmk mentioned that there needs something to be written up. This issue may serve as a place to do that.",
